# Code
```
class Solution {
    public int minInsertions(String s) {
        String rev = new StringBuilder(s).reverse().toString();
        int n = s.length();
        int dp[][] = new int[n + 1][n + 1];
        for(int i = 1; i <= n; i++)
        {
            for(int j = 1; j <= n; j++)
            {
                if(s.charAt(i - 1) == rev.charAt(j - 1))
                {
                    dp[i][j] = dp[i - 1][j - 1] + 1;
                }
                else
                {
                    dp[i][j] = Math.max(dp[i - 1][j], dp[i][j - 1]);
                }
            }
        }
        return n - dp[n][n];
    }
}
```

