**Synopsis:**

Construct the answer `ans` by initializing `ans = [ K ]`, where the input `K` is the first value of the answer.  Then construct the remaining `N - 1` values of the answer by xor'ing each value `x` of the input array `A` with the last value of the answer `ans` so far.

