   We get--> arr[i+1]=encoded[i]^arr[i].***

   ***And arr[0] is given to us. So arr[1]=arr[0]^encoded[0],
   Similarly   arr[i]=arr[i-1]^encoded[i-1]{Starting i from 1}***
